title: AppDynamics: Threads and Requests
agents: appdynamics
catalog: app/java
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check measures the amount of threads of Web Container Runtimes
 using the information collected by AppDynamics. Hence there is no need to
 query the application server itself.

 The WATO ruleset {JVM threads} applies crit/warn levels to the threads part
 of this check.

item:
 Name of the disk and either {{Heap}} or {{Non-Heap}}.

inventory:
 One service for each application.
